3159	  \mathcal{O}_U, -)\); under the corepresentability isomorphism of Lemma~\ref{lem:jshriek_corepr}
3160	  (which is natural in the second variable, being a composite of the sheafification adjunction and
3161	  the free–Yoneda evaluation, both natural), this in turn corresponds to applying \(g\) on sections
